{"tid":1482403,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"用郵寄將文宣貫穿內地","createTime":"2019-08-18T05:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T11:34:17.000Z","uid":171302,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9c08f728060f97d4b1cf98bf30e59dad7805232d","tid":1482403,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:30:11.000Z","msg":"可唔可以用郵寄寄文宣返大陸？<br />\n<br />\n1. 成本平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />($3.4)<br />\n<br />\n2. Random target 所寄的大廈同樓層，重點市鎮，例如北京，上海，深圳，廣州。知識水平較高，收入高，有能有翻場的城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 除非佢拆信逐張睇，否則無可能block 到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 根本Trace唔到邊個寄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 等內地班官媒炒晒車，反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486754adc04dac4c38c74a9596cd79f2c892802e","tid":1482403,"uid":268358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:31:06.000Z","msg":"幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n林鄭自己仆緊街仲想陰d陰d送錢番大陸！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481923</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"880cfb0a951cacd8a76582a41cc722e2e04b8ec3","tid":1482403,"uid":272017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:33:02.000Z","msg":"大慨不可行......<br />\n今日同做順豐的人吹過水，現在不單止在大陸寄去香港的要清關。<br />\n香港寄上大陸都要清關。"},{"pid":"691924cc0d577b0d5131889fd686b8a2f884fe64","tid":1482403,"uid":78885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:33:17.000Z","msg":"推 搵唔到邊個做都想幫手"},{"pid":"09aae22a197cd699d78d009fda8869c159f2f33d","tid":1482403,"uid":272017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"880cfb0a951cacd8a76582a41cc722e2e04b8ec3","tid":1482403,"uid":272017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:33:02.000Z","msg":"大慨不可行......<br />\n今日同做順豐的人吹過水，現在不單止在大陸寄去香港的要清關。<br />\n香港寄上大